<br>
Ned to work on piercing?  Get a dagger of dropping, they go for like 5 copper.   It's 19 delay, and your skill will rise astronomically.<br>
<br>
Need to work on 1hb?  Get a jade mace or Iksar berserker Club, both being relatively cheap, and the same is true.<br>
<br>
Need to work on 2hb?   I had the same problem, my 2hb was sucky, so I decided I'd use 2hb at all times on raids... it worked, every time we'd raid, I'd whip out a 2hb and do crap damage.  It's maxed now.<br>
<br>
Bash?  Find an enchanter with Project: Illusion and ask for trollform, you'll be able to slam and will get your bash skill up.<br>
<br>
Throwing?  Use throwing stuff to pull.<br>
<br>
